snippet.title: PICO-8 Slipways 5 star playthrough on tough
snippet.description:
And I thought I'm done playing vidiya games for good. 
A cute little puzzle/strategy game I've found recently. One of the better games on PICO-8, and it only has a handful of first-time playthroughs on youtube, so here is a more proper one.
